/*----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
 |                                                                            |
 |                                INSTALL                                     |
 |                                                                            |
 +----------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

 It is assumed that you already have Heyu installed and running. If not refer
 to heyu.org for heyu packages and install information.

 1) Unpack into web root
 2) chmod 777 dbs directory
 3) Edit config.inc.php and set paths
 4) Point web browser at webroot and use


 $> chown nobody:nobody smarty/templates_c
$> chown nobody:nobody smarty/cache
$> chmod 775 smarty/templates_c
$> chmod 775 smarty/cache